title: The Check-In: Stephen Miller | Donald J. Trump's Guide To Republican Greatness | Fred Armisen ASMR
description:
Seth checks in on how Stephen Miller is helping carry out Trump's policy agenda.

Then, hear how Donald J. Trump has led the Republican party to greatness, read by someone you may recognize.

Finally, Fred Armisen helps you relax in a new ASMR recording.
